{"pv9:0.1":"Petavatthu ","pv9:0.2":"Uragavagga ","pv9:0.3":"9. Mahapesakarapetivatthu ","pv9:1.1":"“Guthanca muttam ruhiranca pubbam, ","pv9:1.2":"Paribhunjati kissa ayam vipako; ","pv9:1.3":"Ayam nu kim kammamakasi nari, ","pv9:1.4":"Ya sabbada lohitapubbabhakkha. ","pv9:2.1":"Navani vatthani subhani ceva, ","pv9:2.2":"Muduni suddhani ca lomasani; ","pv9:2.3":"Dinnanimissa kitaka bhavanti, ","pv9:2.4":"Ayam nu kim kammamakasi nari”ti. ","pv9:3.1":"“Bhariya mamesa ahu bhadante, ","pv9:3.2":"Adayika maccharini kadariya; ","pv9:3.3":"Sa mam dadantam samanabrahmananam, ","pv9:3.4":"Akkosati ca paribhasati ca. ","pv9:4.1":"‘Guthanca muttam ruhiranca pubbam, ","pv9:4.2":"Paribhunja tvam asucim sabbakalam; ","pv9:4.3":"Etam te paralokasmim hotu, ","pv9:4.4":"Vattha ca te kitakasama bhavantu’; ","pv9:4.5":"Etadisam duccaritam caritva, ","pv9:4.6":"Idhagata cirarattaya khadati”ti. ","pv9:5.1":"Mahapesakarapetivatthu navamam. "}